data.description: **2.75% ASSUMABLE RATE** Welcome to the prestigious ''West Lake'' community within the luxurious Cane Bay Plantation! This exceptional neighborhood stands out among the rest, offering a unique and captivating ambiance that will leave you in awe. As you explore the area, you'll be greeted by a charming home boasting elegance and sophistication.Exuding curb appeal, this residence features a stunning combination of cement plank siding and a brick front, complemented by a long driveway, a two-car garage, and meticulously manicured landscaping. The exterior has been freshly painted in a crisp white hue, adding a touch of modernity to the home. Step inside and be greeted by a grand foyer adorned with wood railing staircases, allowing natural light to flood the space and showcasing the beautiful wood flooring.  The main level offers a seamless flow, starting with a separate dining room adorned with a coffered ceiling, perfect for hosting formal gatherings. Crown molding graces every corner of this exquisite home, while strategically placed windows invite an abundance of sunlight indoors. The open concept living area seamlessly connects to the expansive kitchen, which boasts the largest kitchen plan in all of West Lake.  Prepare to be amazed by the gourmet kitchen, featuring quartz countertops, white craftsman-style cabinetry, and top-of-the-line KitchenAid stainless steel appliances, including a gas stove and double ovens. The exquisite backsplash adds a touch of elegance, while the spacious layout allows for effortless entertaining. Every room in the home has been pre-wired for ceiling fans, ensuring comfort and convenience.  This emerald high-end build offers exceptional insulation, hurricane tiedown cables, and storm protection, providing peace of mind during inclement weather. The main level also features a guest bedroom with a full bathroom, ideal for accommodating visitors. Additionally, a built-in mudroom adds functionality and organization to your daily routine.  As you ascend the oak tread staircase, you'll discover the remaining bedrooms and bathrooms. One of the rooms boasts cathedral ceilings, offering versatility as a bedroom, playroom, movie theater, or media room. The upstairs also features a walk-in laundry room with tiled floors and plumbing ready for a sink installation. Two additional guest bedrooms at the end of the hall share a well-appointed bathroom, complete with quartz countertops and tiled flooring.  The primary bedroom is a true retreat, boasting an oversized layout, tray ceilings, and expansive windows that overlook the serene pond and fountain. The primary bathroom is equally impressive, featuring double vanities, quartz countertops, white cabinetry, a luxurious soaking tub, and a floor-to-ceiling tiled shower. The primary closet offers ample space for all your wardrobe needs.  Step outside and be greeted by a spacious screened-in back porch, perfect for enjoying the outdoors in comfort and privacy. The large yard is fully fenced, providing a safe haven for children and pets to play. The six-foot privacy fence ensures tranquility and seclusion.  The West Lake community offers an array of exceptional amenities, including a sprawling swimming pool, a pickleball court, picnic tables, bocce ball areas, horseshoe pits, a fire pit, a fishing dock, a playground, and a grass field for various sports activities. Additionally, a boat ramp grants access to the expansive 350-acre fishing lake, perfect for kayaking, paddleboarding, or simply enjoying a leisurely boat ride.  The neighborhood is also equipped with golf cart and walking trails that stretch from the back to the front, connecting to nearby schools, restaurants, shopping centers, and grocery stores. Imagine the convenience of hopping on your golf cart and enjoying a delightful dinner with friends and family at the renowned Cane Bay Plantation.  Speaking of Cane Bay Plantation, it is home to the largest YMCA on the entire East Coast, offering an impressive array of amenities such as softball fields, soccer fields, tennis courts, a basketball court, a public library, a gym, Olympic-sized swimming pools, and much more. The neighborhood also hosts food trucks every night of the week and has exciting activities during the holidays, ensuring a vibrant and engaging community atmosphere.  Cane Bay Plantation is truly a one-of-a-kind neighborhood, offering an unparalleled quality of life. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the epitome of luxury living. Schedule a viewing of this remarkable home today and embark on a journey of refined elegance and endless possibilities!
